{{#> container}}
  {{#*inline "email-content"}}
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      This is a gentle reminder that your BYOC region
      <strong
        class="txt-light"
        style="color: #ffffff"
      >{{regionName}}</strong> added to your
      <strong
        class="txt-light"
        style="color: #ffffff"
      >{{workspaceName}}</strong> is not accessible from Patr due to unknown reasons.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      Verify whether the cluster is in active state from your cloud providers dashboard. 
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      If {{regionName}} cluster is already deleted in the cloud provider, then mark this cluster as deleted in 
      <a
        href="https://app.patr.cloud/region/{{regionId}}"
        class="plain-link txt-primary"
        style="color: #f89b41; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;"
      >Patr dashboard</a>.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      If the cluster is not accessible in {{deadlineLimit}} days, then {{regionName}} cluster and the deployments made in that cluster will be marked as deleted in Patr.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      If you are facing any issues, reach out to us at
      <a
        href="mailto:suppport@patr.cloud"
        class="plain-link txt-primary"
        title="Contact Patr support"
        style="color: #f89b41; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;"
      >suppport@patr.cloud</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  {{/inline}}
{{/container}}